Title: Pole Kit for EZ-ZipBlocker or Sunblocker
Content:
Add versatility and another 6' of extension to your RV Awning!

Carefree's NEW Pole Kit features easy to-adjust poles that are capable of handling up to 50 lbs. of pressure without slipping. This pole kit allows use to turn your Carefree SunBlocker, EZ Zip Blocker or other brands and blocker products into an Awning Extension. Instead of staking your blocker down in a vertical position, use our Pole Kit to to raise it up any angle you choose and get yourself a lot more shade without obstructing your view! Easy flip lock for quick and simple height adjustments. Comes with Heavy Duty straps, stakes and storage bag.

Title: Universal White LED 60 LPM Replacement Awning Light Strip
Content:
Universal White 60 LPM LED Replacement Light Strip

Replacement LED light strip for all brands of RV Awnings. 60 LPM (Lights-Per-meter) White 3M adhesive backed LED Replacement light strip. Strip is 16' long with a 26" long wire lead and can easily be trimmed to fit. Comes with a 2-prong plug for replacement on Carefree awnings, or for use with Lippert and Dometic awnings, simply cut off the 2-prong plug and connect to wires using the included butt-splice wire connectors. .

Title: Black Automatic Awning Support Cradle
Content:
Automatic Awning Support Cradle

Color-BLACK. Works with all brands of RV Awnings. Rollers on all brands of longer awnings will have a tendency to bounce and flex during travel. This can over time lead to the roller taking a permanent set, causing wobbly roll-up and an undesirable canopy. The Carefree Awning Support Cradle receives the roller and supports it eliminating sag. Unroll the awning and the Automatic Support Cradle releases the roller and pivots open, ready to accept the roller again. The patented support action of our unique cradle receives the roller and gently supports it eliminating all the weight and natural sag in the middle of the roller. Easy to install and go, no need to tension this awning support after you roll up the awning! Please note: Will not work on awnings with Uniguard.

Title: White Straight Rafters (BOGO)
Content:
* Fits awnings with roller tubes with an 8' extension

Carefree's new Rafters are designed to add rigidity and further support to your awning. Installing the Rafter is simple and easy. It does not require a drill for installation unlike most rafters available today as it hooks directly to your awning rail and with the quick turn of the locking knob, the rafter quickly extends to fit snugly against the roll bar. Carefree rafters also include an industry first utility slot to quickly hang side blockers, side panels or other awning accessories.

Title: Awning Stabiliz'r
Content:
Carefree's Awning Stabiliz'r is two support poles designed to offer further support to the Latitude, Longitude or Travel'r awnings during periods of prolonged usage or extended stays at your campsite.


No drilling or dealer installation required! Quick, easy set-up as poles have an adjustment lever to quickly set them to the desired height. The Awning Stabiliz'r Pole Kit also includes stakes and straps to ensure a secure fit.

Download the Awning Stabiliz'r Pole Kit manual

Title: HD Awning Stabiliz'r
Content:
The HD Awning Stabiliz'r is a new, Heavy-Duty version of the Awning Stabiliz'r pole kit and provides vertical support to your awning. It is the first pole kit to accommodate both box awnings and awnings with roll bars, with the versatility of fitting Carefree and competitive brand awnings. It comes standard with stakes and tie-downs to secure the poles to the awning and the ground. Want to further stabilize your awning in less than 5 minutes? The HD Awning Stabiliz'r is your solution!

Cradle

For awnings with roll bars

For securing pole kit to a box awning

Crank Knob

Used to secure pole kit after adjusting the height

Stakes and Straps

To secure poles to ground and awning

Title: Universal White LED Add-On Awning Light Kit-White with Remote
Content:
Universal White LED Awning Add-On Light Kit

Be the envy of the campsite with adjustable light that is bright enough to read by. These fun, 3M adhesive-backed energy saving dimmable LEDs are great for parties or just enjoying the evening outside. These lights can attach to your awning, the side of your RV or just about anywhere you want them. Simple installation: no drilling or dealer installation required! Fits all brands of RV Awnings, does not require a specialty awning roller tube.


Kit Includes: 1-16' Spool of White LED lights with 3M adhesive backed peel-and-stick strip (easy trim to fit), Waterproof RF receiver, Handheld Remote, 12V Hardwired Plug, 110V Plug

Title: White Anti-Flap Kit
Content:
This product is on sale! Originally $349.99 + $15.00 Shipping, now $299 + Free Shipping!

The Anti-Flap kit by Carefree of Colorado is designed to clamp onto each side of your awning canopy, making it more taught and helping eliminate excessive canopy movement that can damage the awning hardware. It will also offer added rigidity and support to your awning. It is designed to work with both manual and powered awnings and features an easy twist knob to secure the rafter in place. Designed to fit awnings with an 8' projection only. Available in black and white hardware.

Title: Thin-Lite Hanger, clip
Content:
Use this clip to hang your Carefree Thin-Lite with non-Spirit Utility slot roller tubes.

If your awning does not feature the Spirit Thin-Lite Utility slot, and you wish to use the Carefree Thin-Lite fluorescent light, you will need these clips. Simply unroll the awning, slide 2 Thin-Lite hanger clips into the open lower slot of the roller tube and snap the lights into the clips. 

Important Note: The Thin-Lite and the clips must be removed before the awning is retracted.

*Available while supplies last

Title: Fiesta HD Remote Lock Kit Orange
Fiesta HD Remote Lock Kit White
Eclipse XL arm set - Black
Content:
The Eclipse XL offers the strongest arm set of any Carefree awning while also boasting a longer 9' extension. This means you get more shade and coverage next to your RV! The Eclipse XL is retrofittable so you can upgrade your existing manual awning to a powered awning or your existing Dometic or Solera roller assemblies to unsurpassed durability and performance. Just swap out the arm set!

The Eclipse is also technology compatible. What does this mean? It means that you can install Carefree Connects Wireless Awning Control System (Link this please) and control your new Eclipse XL using the Carefree Connects mobile app on your favorite smart device. The Carefree Connects system is Bluetooth enabled allowing easy connection and maximum control of your awning from the comfort of your chair! No more getting up to adjust your awning!

Eclipse XL arm sets come in either black or white hardware with lengths from 8' to 21'. It requires a flat, unobstructed 70' x 4.5' mounting area for each arm to retrofit to your RV.

Eclipse XL roller assemblies come standard with Carefree's one-of-a-kind FLXguard fabric protection to ensure the longevity of your new awning fabric.

Title: White Cradle
Content:
Automatic Awning Support Cradle

Works with all brands of RV Awnings. Rollers on all brands of longer awnings will have a tendency to bounce and flex during travel. This can over time lead to the roller taking a permanent set, causing wobbly roll-up and an undesirable canopy. The Carefree Awning Support Cradle receives the roller and supports it eliminating sag. Unroll the awning and the Automatic Support Cradle releases the roller and pivots open, ready to accept the roller again. The patented support action of our unique cradle receives the roller and gently supports it eliminating all the weight and natural sag in the middle of the roller. Easy to install and go, no need to tension this awning support after you roll up the awning! Please note: Will not work on awnings with Uniguard.

Title: 6', White, Simply Shade Window Awning
Content:
DIY Installation!

NEW! The Simply Shade Window Awning is the first window awning designed for DIY installation. Now you no longer have to custom order your window awning. In fact, you do not even need to wait for your window awning to be delivered as the Simply Shade Window Awning is a cash and carry product that you can buy and install in the same day!


Available in 2 standard color options; black hardware with a black vinyl fabric or white hardware with a white vinyl fabric. It comes in 3' - 6' lengths with increments by the half foot and works for windows up to 36" tall.


Simply Shade Window Awning includes awning rail, arms, roller assembly and fabric, all necessary mounting hardware and DIY installation instructions.

Simply Shade Window Awning includes awning rail, arms, roller assembly and fabric, all necessary mounting hardware and DIY installation instructions.

Title: PIN HOLE PRO - WHITE
Content:
Specially formulated vinyl repair compound specific to Carefree vinyl fabrics.

Pin Hole Pro is a specially forumalted vinyl repair compound used to fix voids (pin holes) up to 1/8" in Carefree's vinyl fabric. Simple to use as all you need to do is gently place a drop directly onto the void and let dry and your canopy is fixed!.

please note: we are unable to ship VLP and Pin Hole Pro via Airfreight due to Hazmat restrictions

Title: Pioneer End Cap Upgrade Kit-Black or White (select color)
Content:
Convert your existing Carefree Spirit, Fiesta or Simplicity spring driven awning to a simple manual crank-out awning!

If your current awning fabric, arms and roller are in good condition, this Pioneer End Cap Upgrade Kit can be installed to simply convert your awning to an easy to operate manual-crank version. Never worry about springs and spring tension again. Your awning springs will be removed and replaced with this upgrade kit. The crank mechanism assembly is installed on the front arm and the idler on the rear awning arm.

Note: the telescoping crank handle is sold separately

Order Now

Title: Alpine Slideout Cover
Content:
Works with Sliderooms from 42″ – 336″ (28′) in length!

The Alpine SOC works with the longest sliderooms available on the market today. It boasts larger brackets for improved stability and operation. It also features internal locks that do not require any adjustments or settings prior to operation which also offer improved anti-billowing. The Alpine SOC also features end caps designed to cover more of the internal components improving the aesthetics of both the awning and your RV!

Title: Apex Replacement Canopy
Content: The Apex Patio Awning offers the coach owner an awning system that provides as much or as little shade as required. The canopies are housed in an aluminum case that easily blends in with the coach roof. Each unit is equipped with Apex lateral support arms that are the strongest available on the market. No vertical arms interfere with coach sidewalls or equipment that may be mounted on the roof. These arms can also be adjusted to vary the canopy pitch up to 3 feet (it is strongly recommended that service and adjustments be performed by trained technicians). The unique and innovative 110V electronic control system provides Carefree’s newest Direct Response system with interior pushbutton controls for standard extend/retract functions. At the master control panel the auto-retract system can be engaged to automatically retract the awning in windy conditions. Sensitivity can be set to respond to a variety of wind speed conditions. An RF remote is furnished with the Direct Response system. Apex is an OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) product available on select motor homes only, ask the manufacturer of your choice to include the Paramount or Apex awning systems on your next motor home purchase. Replacement Parts Replace Canopy

Title: Ascent Slide Out Awning
Content:
The Ascent is the newest innovative slide awning addition to the Carefree line with many added features and benefits:

  • Performance… Improved pitch provides the industry’s best rain run off.
  • Style… blends smoothly with the coach wall, the Ascent matches all other Carefree styled products for a uniform look throughout the RV.
  • Quality… Fast and accurate installation. All mounting hardware concealed for a clean finished look.
  • Value… The Ascent room mounted roller helps protect the value of your investment by drawing debris away from your coach! Available in standard and extra long (XL) models.
  • Removable hinged cover feature means easy access for cleaning and service. Invented by and exclusive to Carefree of Colorado.
  • Hardware colors include white and black.
  • Available in three fabrics: acrylic, polyweave and vinyl.
Configure Product Replacement Parts Replace Canopy

Title: Awning Extend'r
Content:
The Awning Extend’r extends the canopy of your awning; giving you more covered space next to your RV! The canopy included with the Awning Extend’r extends the shade of your awning by eight feet. No drilling or dealer installation required! Quick, easy set-up. Fits all manual and 12V awnings with an empty slot in the roller tube. Kit includes adjustable support poles, stakes and straps to secure the fabric extension to the ground. Also included is a lightweight, convenient carry bag for easy storage while not in use. Available in 12’, 14’ 16’, 18’ and 20’ lengths and an 8’ extension. Use caution when using with any awning that has an automatic retract function. See Awning Owners Manual for specific details.

Title: Eclipse 12V Patio Awning
Content:
Eclipse is the industry’s 1st 12V power awning that features instant pitch adjustments!

Push and hold the button to extend the Eclipse to partial or full 8′ extension in just seconds. As the billow-proof worm-gear motor unrolls the canopy, the rafter arms glide up the vertical track on the side of the coach to deploy a stable, truss-like, overhead support.

Push and hold the button to retract and the Eclipse will roll up tight against the coach. That’s it! There’s nothing to lock or latch. Carefree’s exclusive worm-gear drive motor locks the roller for travel and provides the greatest assurance of absolute protection against billowing.

Buy a complete Eclipse or upgrade your existing Carefree or A&E roller assembly with a 12V Eclipse Arm Set!

Title: Fiesta Manual Patio Awning
Content:
A Premium Awning at a Great Price!

The Fiesta Awning looks better, lasts longer and has proven itself over and over again with years of outstanding performance over competitive spring loaded awning brands. The Fiesta features the strongest arm channels and highest quality fabrics available. Don’t settle for the competitor’s less rigid awnings-Demand the Fiesta Awning for complete peace of mind in a spring loaded awning.

Title: Freedom Roof Mount Box Awning
Content:
No Latches to Unlock

The Freedom Roof Mount has all the same features and benefits as the wall mount version, except instead of mounting to the side of your unit, it mounts up on the roof. As it opens the arms unfold as you turn the hand crank or push a button (12 volt models only). The support arms fold out of the lead bar once it’s at eye level and within easy reach. The support arms adjust easily with flip lock controls to adjust for awning height. To close, just fold the support arms up into the lead rail and crank in the opposite direction – or simply push a button on the motorized awning; the awning case closes and locks automatically. The 12V model includes a manual override if power is lost.

Configure Product Replacement Parts Replace Canopy

Title: Freedom Wall Mount Box Awning
Content:
Sleek, Easy to Operate

The Freedom Wall Mount Awning is a box awning that mounts to the side of your truck camper or RV. It opens and the arms unfold as you turn the hand crank or push a button (12 volt models only). The support arms fold out of the lead bar once it’s at eye level and within easy reach. The support arms adjust easily with flip lock controls. To close, just fold the support arms up into the lead rail and crank in the opposite direction – or simply push a button on the motorized awning; the awning case closes and locks automatically. The 12V model includes a manual override if power is lost.

Title: Paramount Canopy Replacement
Content:
Three Awnings in One!

No more multiple awnings with Carefree’s NEW Paramount!

This smart new awning has three positions to protect your RV: Slideout, Slideout & Window, and Full Patio Extension. No need for multiple awnings on the RV! This box awning also mounts on top of the RV and doesn’t interfere with the side wall, side wall graphics, windows or accessories. The Paramount is also available for single, double or quadruple installation. The Direct Response auto-retraction system is included to help prevent wind/weather damage. The Paramount features a newly designed master control panel and remote control.

Paramount is an OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) product available on select motor homes only, ask the manufacturer of your choice to include the Paramount or Apex awning systems on your next motor home purchase.

Replacement Parts
Replace Canopy

Title: Pioneer
Content:
Quick, Easy, Manual Operation

The Carefree Pioneer manual awning is the easiest full size patio awning to operate. No need to worry about unlocking travel locks or spring mechanisms with this awning. To open the Pioneer, simply turn the hand crank. Once it is fully open, slide the single track slider arm up to the roller and tighten the rafter knobs. Now you can raise the roller with the lift handles to any desired pitch. It’s that simple. For an exceptionally taut canopy, backwind the crank to make your canopy as tight as a drum. There’s never a need to re-tension your canopy. In breezy conditions, the worm gear mechanism will not allow your roller to unwind. When finished using your awning, lower the roller tube, loosen the rafter knobs and slide the rafter arms to the closed position. Just turn the hand crank in the opposite direction until the roller is tight against the coach and you’re ready for travel. That’s it. There’s no locks or straps to fuss with to prevent billowing in transit. The crank assembly automatically locks the roller in place. Available in all fabric styles and colors including Carefree’s patented no leak Alumaguard or Uniguard.

Title: Truckin' Awn
Content:
Protect your entrance door rain or shine!

Now you can leave your door open in just about any weather.

Configure

Title: Vacation'r
Content:
Lightweight design in a high quality room!

For all brands of traditional and Carefree 12v awnings

This lightweight room is specifically designed to fit the Carefree 12v Eclipse and Travel’r as well as all brands of traditional patio awnings. Set-up is fast and easy with Carefree’s Vacation’r room design. There are no poles, rafters or permanent fasteners to attach to your coach. Features include multi-setting privacy panels, ground stakes, tall skirting for the open areas under the RV and a zippered tote-style storage bag. See your dealer for availability and pricing.

Configure Product

Content:
Awning Rail for Mounting Patio Awnings, SL Window Awnings, Truckin Awn, SOKII, SOKIII & Slide Out Cover Awnings.

Aluminum awning rail. Please select color and size needed for installation. Does not include mounting hardware or sealant. Awning rail accepts 1/4" Standard Polycord. Sections longer than 8' must ship via truck freight. Works with most all brands of RV awnings.
